{"tid":1054621,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"【哈利波特】躲在廁所的愛哭鬼麥朵　真實年紀竟嚇親一眾影迷！","createTime":"2019-03-10T03:05:33.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-10T10:13:08.000Z","uid":130626,"like":25,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"3151b4ed54829d3ca99f0e9c8562daeba1908a2b","tid":1054621,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-10T03:05:33.000Z","msg":"《哈利波特》電影系列深入民心，當中除了一眾主角為人熟悉，其實不少配角也在影迷心中留下很深刻的印象。而提到經常躲在霍格華茲廁所裡哭的幽靈，相信大家都能立即回想起那個畫面，眨下眼原來飾演愛哭鬼麥朵（Moaning Myrtle）的Shirley Henderson已經53歲，不少影迷知道她的真實年紀都非常驚訝！<br />\n最近，Shirley Henderson更在新戲中扮演喜劇天團的老婆，依舊年輕的外表，令不少影迷都大讚，她絕對可以被封為《哈利波特》中的美魔女。<br />\n愛哭鬼麥朵是《哈利波特》系列中的，相當令人難忘的角色。這位女學生生前被蛇妖殺死後就變成了幽靈，生活在霍格華茲的2樓女廁裡，據知有時候更會去男生浴場偷窺。在小說裡，愛哭鬼麥朵在很多集都有現身，不過講到電影版的《哈利波特》，她就主要在《哈利波特：消失的密室》和《哈利波特：火盃的考驗》有戲份。<br />\n<br />\n早前與榮恩再同框出現<br />\n而其實Shirley Henderson在17年前上映《哈利波特：消失的密室》中扮演愛哭鬼麥朵時，已經有37歲，但當年扮起中學生也毫無違和感！現年53歲的Shirley Henderson可說是依然保養得宜，早前與「榮恩」Rupert Grint再度合體，拍攝BBC電視劇《The ABC Murders》，不只影迷興奮，連榮恩都話十多年後再合作，可以在片場遇見熟悉的面孔感覺很好。<br />\n而Shirley Henderson最新的作品，就是在新戲《Stan &amp; Ollie》中，夥拍約翰韋利（John C.Reilly）演兩公婆。電影《Stan &amp; Ollie》改編自搞笑二人組Stan Laurel和Oliver Hardy的故事，找來約翰韋利飾演Oliver Hardy。據知，原本劇組想找知名度更高的演員來當Oliver Hardy的老婆，但約翰韋利就推薦Shirley，為此她更多次去到倫敦試鏡，最終也因為演技精湛而接了這角色。而Shirley亦透露拍檔約翰萊利身型很高大，在他身邊演出感覺特別安心，加上二人相識很久，很有默契，合作得心應手。<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/2529898/org/99c297fa99b7a08cfab7a7e63f53f394.jpg/laXXY7FNbRvmPh1D0yj2usvjWEk6fyvfF7I6tReyOrU\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F2529898%2Forg%2F99c297fa99b7a08cfab7a7e63f53f394.jpg%2FlaXXY7FNbRvmPh1D0yj2usvjWEk6fyvfF7I6tReyOrU&h=9799c769&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/2529900/org/0b20315b1b67c57baf754ae2d208b75e.png/hrcziiFH9KukC9OfRmVc8nZv3TZNhMLEaxvnWGsb51g\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F2529900%2Forg%2F0b20315b1b67c57baf754ae2d208b75e.png%2FhrcziiFH9KukC9OfRmVc8nZv3TZNhMLEaxvnWGsb51g&h=2df7d966&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/2529896/org/974a61f7fcdff36b8a83854bd8c3f754.jpg/vVl78Sh1l0VUy7k2r4oTOI7Z6tp6-tXMHK7Zqhyu2ao\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F2529896%2Forg%2F974a61f7fcdff36b8a83854bd8c3f754.jpg%2FvVl78Sh1l0VUy7k2r4oTOI7Z6tp6-tXMHK7Zqhyu2ao&h=6fe85ad4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/2529906/org/e54e52b9604ce7589f06e583074aa21e.jpg/Wa2VAzctLP9Qv1cOI2pa1iNKJt3pYgw8iegUNYnoFDU\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F2529906%2Forg%2Fe54e52b9604ce7589f06e583074aa21e.jpg%2FWa2VAzctLP9Qv1cOI2pa1iNKJt3pYgw8iegUNYnoFDU&h=b0eaca5f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"08116d704210fbb2ae2a3db73f424fa8b8b2b922","tid":1054621,"uid":194461,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-10T06:18:24.000Z","msg":"佢就係sherlok 入面個雪筣？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"63b25f03ce6309ecb73b30bd1071385fcee39682","tid":1054621,"uid":168366,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-10T06:21:28.000Z","msg":"痴線 真實幾正喎"},{"pid":"77ff848ba5af637b981078c474ada5eb676b577d","tid":1054621,"uid":81113,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-10T06:21:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bang.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3ad4a52c92f440903ffae3fa779000fe8ca00625","tid":1054621,"uid":202256,"like":1,"dislike":4,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-10T06:28:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><br />\n早前與「榮恩」Rupert Grint<span style=\"color: red;\">再度合體</span>，拍攝BBC電視劇《The ABC Murders》，不只影迷興奮，連榮恩都話十多年後再合作，可以在片場遇見熟悉的面孔感覺很好。<br />\n</blockquote><br />\n乜撚野再度合體<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 01啲妓者<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"161